    <title>Shortnen URL</title>
    <p>To make a request to the shortening endpoint simply make an HTTP GET request to the endpoint <code>/create/</code> with the <code>URL</code> parameter set to the target URL (the URL to be shortened).</p>
    <p>The final URL should look like this:</p>
    <code-block lang="http">https://api.reknag.com/create/?url=[TARGET_URL]</code-block>
    Where:
    <table style="none">
        <tr>
            <td>[TARGET_URL]</td>
            <td>The URL to be shortened</td>
        </tr>
    </table>
